  howToUse: "Place a TutorialPopup script on the object that   \nneeds to appear
    and drag that object into the TutorialList in the order that you want them to
    appear. \nMake a unity event for the event you want to trigger going to the next
    popup with \nPress the plus under the unity event and add the tutorial popup
    object\nMake it trigger the Next function to go to the next popup. \nMake it
    trigger back to go to a previous popup; leave it null to go the one before the
    current\n"
